{"tid":1094874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Amazon 將發射三千多枚衛星 向全球提供網絡服務","createTime":"2019-04-06T15:33:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T03:01:32.000Z","uid":48083,"like":93,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"c4532eaaa8ee591a8d3f30134e6d105fe8304d75","tid":1094874,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T15:33:26.000Z","msg":"先進國家的互聯網普及率已達到飽和，要繼續增加網絡覆蓋率，傳統的方式成本太高昂，用近地衛星就相對簡單。最近有報導指 Amazon 計劃發射大量衛星，把互聯網服務覆蓋到全球。<br />\n<br />\n據消息指，Amazon 打算進行一個名為「Project Kuiper」的計劃，發射 3,236 枚網絡衛星到三個不同高度的近地軌道，包括地面以上 590 公里的 784 枚衛星、610 公里的 1,296 枚衛星，以及 629 公里的 1,156 枚衛星。Amazon 方面已經向 FCC 提交申請。他們表示，這個計劃是為了全球未得到基本互聯網連接，或服務不足的地方帶來高速寬頻網絡服務，未來會繼續尋找合作夥伴。<br />\n<br />\nAmazon 未提及相關的衛星發射計劃會否與總裁 Jeff Bezos 自己的 Blue Origin 合作，表示將會考慮不同的選擇。除了 Amazon 之外，其實 Google 和 Facebook，以及 SpaceX 等公司也有計劃開發類似的全球衛星寬頻網絡服務，未來這類服務會否因為競爭而降低收費門檻，實在令人期待。<br />\n<br />\n來源：GeekWire<br />\n<br />\n﻿ &bull; 不想錯過新科技 ? 請 Follow <a href=\"http://unwire.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk&d=174aH8n0e8hd5Ixdtq%2FhYjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=994edd41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">unwire.hk</a> FB 專頁<a href=\"http://facebook.com/unwirehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Funwirehk%2F&d=174aH8n0e8hd5Ixdtq%2FhYjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=0f40c85c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://facebook.com/unwirehk/</a><br />\n&bull; 要入手生活科技潮物 即上 unwire store <br />\n<a href=\"https://store.unwire.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.unwire.hk%2F&d=174aH8n0e8hd5Ixdtq%2FhYjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=7cd3f1a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.unwire.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/04/06/amazon-project-kuiper-broadband-satellite/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F04%2F06%2Famazon-project-kuiper-broadband-satellite%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=174aH8n0e8hd5Ixdtq%2FhYjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=12fb3558\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/04/06/amazon-project-kuiper-broadband-satellite/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"230bf472e6bf4e615655e561cb3b0d01184a2ef5","tid":1094874,"uid":63113,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T15:36:21.000Z","msg":"好似同類計劃講過好多次 真係射電訊界會唔會經濟崩潰"},{"pid":"e5b11226534eab8854f28cb354bdcdc86f89ba1a","tid":1094874,"uid":68787,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T15:40:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ecf64880c4c23533bd9a6fa16341e0395e5d583c","tid":1094874,"uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"230bf472e6bf4e615655e561cb3b0d01184a2ef5","tid":1094874,"uid":63113,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T15:36:21.000Z","msg":"好似同類計劃講過好多次 真係射電訊界會唔會經濟崩潰"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T15:40:17.000Z","msg":"之前google話做<br />\n唔知點解冇咗"},{"pid":"a3378d870b9a7ce224896ba57ec6ae60ce75edb6","tid":1094874,"uid":68787,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T15:41:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7f36035b74eb82c464f49b0aff83ab30597b67b","tid":1094874,"uid":89514,"like":55,"dislike":2,"score":53,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T15:41:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62c9690eba8c8681177b337bd818f0975746757f","tid":1094874,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":36,"score":-36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T15:42:45.000Z","msg":"華為6g既plan都係咁上下<br />\n<br />\n此外，華為甚至設想發射10,000多顆小型低軌衞星，實現覆蓋全球6G通訊的設想，並且估算了成本：99億美元。至於何時才能將6G技術落實到日常應用中，華為5G產品線總裁楊超斌曾在博鰲亞洲論壇上表示，從2018年發佈5G第一個標準以來，華為跟中國、韓國、歐洲、中東等多間運營商合作，已可完成大帶寬、高速度的測試，速率確定可以提升10倍左右。5G是未來10年到20年的主流，6G要來也是2030年之後的事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190401/59438844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190401%2F59438844&d=174aH8n0e8hd5Ixdtq%2FhYjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=7c704bdc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%